"version": "1.0.4",
"title": "5565: suffering, of believers",
"media_type": "Text",
"index_reference": "5565",
"language": "eng",
"review_level": "None",
"content": "<p>Believers ought to expect to suffer as an inevitable part of their calling. To believe is not to evade suffering; it is to face it with new confidence and hope. Rightly approached, suffering develops the character of believers, equips them for more effective service, draws believers closer to Jesus Christ and prepares them for eternal life.</p>\n<h2>Believers must expect suffering</h2>\n<h3>Jesus Christ foretold it</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt10:22\">MAT 10:22</a></strong> parallel <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mark13:13\">MRK 13:13</a> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt10:17\">MAT 10:17</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt23:34\">MAT 23:34</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt24:9\">MAT 24:9</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke21:16-Luke21:17\">LUK 21:16–21:17</a></p>\n<h3>The apostles foretold it</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts14:22\">ACT 14:22</a></strong>; <strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Tim3:12\">2TI 3:12</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Phil1:29\">PHP 1:29</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1John3:13\">1JN 3:13</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rev2:10\">REV 2:10</a></p>\n<h3>The experience of the OT shows it</h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rom8:36\">ROM 8:36</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Heb11:25-Heb11:26\">HEB 11:25–11:26</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Heb11:32-Heb11:38\">HEB 11:32–11:38</a></p>\n<h3>The experience of the NT shows it</h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts4:3\">ACT 4:3</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts5:40\">ACT 5:40</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts9:29\">ACT 9:29</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts12:1-Acts12:3\">ACT 12:1–12:3</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Cor11:23-2Cor11:29\">2CO 11:23–11:29</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gal3:4\">GAL 3:4</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Thess2:2\">1TH 2:2</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Thess2:14\">1TH 2:14</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Pet4:4\">1PE 4:4</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Heb10:32-Heb10:34\">HEB 10:32–10:34</a></p>\n<h2>Suffering for Jesus Christ is commendable</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt5:10-Matt5:12\">MAT 5:10–5:12</a></strong> parallel <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke6:20-Luke6:23\">LUK 6:20–6:23</a> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts5:41\">ACT 5:41</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Tim1:8\">2TI 1:8</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Pet2:19\">1PE 2:19</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Pet3:17\">1PE 3:17</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Pet4:12-1Pet4:16\">1PE 4:12–4:16</a></p>\n<h2>Suffering is profitable</h2>\n<h3>It affirms believers' adoption</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Heb12:7\">HEB 12:7</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/John15:19\">JHN 15:19</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/John17:14\">JHN 17:14</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rom8:17\">ROM 8:17</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gal6:17\">GAL 6:17</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Thess1:4-2Thess1:5\">2TH 1:4–1:5</a></p>\n<h3>It is the price of godliness</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Heb12:11\">HEB 12:11</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps119:67\">PSA 119:67</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps119:71\">PSA 119:71</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa38:17\">ISA 38:17</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/John15:2\">JHN 15:2</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Pet1:6-1Pet1:7\">1PE 1:6–1:7</a></p>\n<h3>It is a condition of service</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Cor4:10\">2CO 4:10</a></strong>; <strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Col1:24\">COL 1:24</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps126:5-Ps126:6\">PSA 126:5–126:6</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts9:16\">ACT 9:16</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts20:23-Acts20:24\">ACT 20:23–20:24</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Cor4:9-1Cor4:13\">1CO 4:9–4:13</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Cor1:3-2Cor1:5\">2CO 1:3–1:5</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gal4:19\">GAL 4:19</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Phil3:18\">PHP 3:18</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Col2:1\">COL 2:1</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Tim1:11-2Tim1:12\">2TI 1:11–1:12</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Tim2:3\">2TI 2:3</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Tim2:10\">2TI 2:10</a></p>\n<h3>It develops trust</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Cor1:9\">2CO 1:9</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Pet4:19\">1PE 4:19</a></p>\n<h3>It develops character</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rom5:3-Rom5:4\">ROM 5:3–5:4</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Heb5:8\">HEB 5:8</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jas1:3\">JAS 1:3</a></p>\n<h3>It deepens fellowship</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Cor12:26\">1CO 12:26</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rom12:15\">ROM 12:15</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Cor1:7\">2CO 1:7</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Cor8:2\">2CO 8:2</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gal4:14-Gal4:15\">GAL 4:14–4:15</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gal6:2\">GAL 6:2</a></p>\n<h3>It draws believers to the Lord</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Phil3:8\">PHP 3:8</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Phil3:10\">PHP 3:10</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Job42:5\">JOB 42:5</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Cor4:8-2Cor4:10\">2CO 4:8–4:10</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Cor12:9-2Cor12:10\">2CO 12:9–12:10</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Pet4:13\">1PE 4:13</a></p>\n<h3>It prepares believers for heaven</h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Cor4:16-2Cor5:4\">2CO 4:16–5:4</a></p>",
